{"_id":"4247b4d7cc8b7506","name":"Measured Response","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Henry","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Friendship rank 3+)","description":"When your Digimon is attacked, if you have not taken your turn yet this round, you may use a Free Action to grant your Digimon +3 to their Reliability for that attack only."}}
{"_id":"1b9530f3b8931d8a","name":"Tactical Restraint","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Henry","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Friendship rank 3+)","description":"Once per encounter as a Free Action on your turn, choose one enemy Digimon within 6 spaces. That enemy's Speed is treated as 2 lower when determining turn order next round."}}
{"_id":"89f815abb7547241","name":"Calculated Peace","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Henry","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Friendship rank 4","description":"Once per encounter as your Basic Action, you may attempt to de-escalate a non-boss enemy. Make a Rally skill check DN 16. On a success the enemy skips their next action. This does not work on enemies that have been attacked this encounter."}}
{"_id":"9428ce588da5a853","name":"Cover Fire","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Henry","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Friendship rank 4","description":"Once per encounter when an ally Digimon within 4 spaces is targeted, your Digimon may make a single Basic Attack against that attacker as a Free Action before the attack resolves."}}
{"_id":"ae192b22c9847529","name":"Last Resort","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Henry","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Calculated Peace, Friendship rank 5","description":"Once per encounter as your Basic Action, Henry's Digimon takes a completely defensive stance. Until the start of Henry's next turn all damage dealt to any allied Digimon within 3 spaces is reduced by your Friendship rank. Your Digimon cannot attack while the stance is active."}}
{"_id":"f3b4c0b538ad95a5","name":"Momentai","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Henry","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Cover Fire, Friendship rank 5","description":"Once per session as a Free Action, you may declare Momentai. All allies within 6 spaces who can hear you immediately remove one negative status effect."}}
{"_id":"9ef79fb67f1a6873","name":"The Hardest Kind of Strong","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Henry","row":4,"expCost":1000,"requirements":"Both Row 3 abilities, Friendship rank 7","description":"Once per session at the start of an encounter, before any turns begin, you may declare your intent not to initiate offensive action this encounter. While you have not attacked — your Digimon has not targeted an enemy with a damage-dealing move — all allied Digimon gain +2 to Reliability and +2 to their Love stat for damage reduction. The moment your Digimon deals damage the bonus ends."}}
{"_id":"abc5cb200e55f90b","name":"Gentle Presence","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Jeri","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Love rank 3+)","description":"When you use the Mend skill on an ally — Tamer or Digimon — add your Love rank as a flat bonus to the result on top of the normal skill formula."}}
{"_id":"7708e891026d5588","name":"Leomon's Lesson","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Jeri","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Love rank 3+)","description":"Once per encounter when your Digimon is at 25% HP or below they may use their Move Action as a Free Action this round."}}
{"_id":"c14284bbb4a1e1c1","name":"Hold On","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Jeri","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Love rank 4","description":"Once per encounter when your Digimon would trigger the cascade at Default Stage, you may spend 6 Hope to have them stabilise at 1 HP instead. Default Stage does not drop."}}
{"_id":"a0daf8d416930b12","name":"Puppet Show","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Jeri","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Love rank 4","description":"Once per encounter as a Free Action, you may use your puppet to distract one enemy within 4 spaces. That enemy takes -2 to their next attack roll."}}
{"_id":"67253517e6319546","name":"Grief and Light","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Jeri","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Hold On, Love rank 5","description":"Once per session at the start of your turn you may spend 5 Hope. All allied Digimon immediately restore HP equal to your Love rank x 2. This does not cost your Basic Action."}}
{"_id":"ad2a14c6430e51d6","name":"What Leomon Taught Me","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Jeri","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Leomon's Lesson, Love rank 5","description":"When your Digimon is at 50% HP or below they may use moves they know from one stage higher than their current stage. Stage lock rules are suspended for your Digimon only while this condition is active."}}
{"_id":"49018dccbe5b102b","name":"Still Here","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Jeri","row":4,"expCost":1000,"requirements":"Both Row 3 abilities, Love rank 7","description":"Once per session when your partner Digimon is reduced to 0 HP, you may immediately activate Still Here. The cascade resolves normally — but before it does, restore HP to your Digimon equal to your Love rank. Then immediately take a bonus turn outside of normal turn order. This bonus turn does not count toward your turn in the current round."}}
{"_id":"5c993b13be72f992","name":"Trash Talk","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Kazu","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Reliability rank 3+)","description":"Once per encounter as a Free Action on your turn, choose one visible enemy. That enemy must succeed on a Firewall skill check DN 12 or take -2 to their next attack roll."}}
{"_id":"386d17d2a43a1b6f","name":"Guardromon's Partner","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Kazu","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Reliability rank 3+)","description":"Once per encounter as a Free Action, when an allied Digimon within your Friendship rank x 2 spaces is about to take damage, you may swap places with that Digimon and take the damage yourself instead. The damage number is whatever was going to be applied to the ally — it is not recalculated through your own resistances, weaknesses, or Love stat. You simply take the number."}}
{"_id":"5df7205fa237988b","name":"All In","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Kazu","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Reliability rank 4","description":"Once per encounter before your Digimon makes an attack roll, you may declare All In. Double the damage dice on that attack if it hits. If it misses, your Digimon cannot make any attacks next round — they are completely off balance."}}
{"_id":"2057bdf795c93412","name":"Comeback Kid","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Kazu","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Reliability rank 4","description":"When your Digimon misses an attack roll, their next attack roll this encounter gains +4."}}
{"_id":"6a0a0ffeca0211b9","name":"Better Than I Look","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Kazu","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"All In, Reliability rank 5","description":"All In no longer causes your Digimon to lose their next round's attacks on a miss — they take -2 to their next attack roll instead."}}
{"_id":"a66bebb54decfc5a","name":"Cheerleader","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Kazu","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Comeback Kid, Reliability rank 5","description":"Once per encounter as a Free Action on your turn, choose one enemy Digimon. Until the start of your next turn all allied Digimon that attack that target gain +1 to their attack rolls against it."}}
{"_id":"0ed1465706de3d3e","name":"I Read About This","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Kenta","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Knowledge rank 3+)","description":"Once per session at the start of an encounter, you automatically learn one piece of information about one enemy of your choice — their Attribute, their Element, or whether they are stronger or weaker than your Digimon overall. No check required."}}
{"_id":"4220e4ccc0b7da44","name":"Unlikely Protector","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Kenta","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Knowledge rank 3+)","description":"Once per encounter when an ally Tamer within 2 spaces takes damage that would reduce them to 0 HP, you may spend 4 Hope to take half that damage yourself instead — rounding the halved amount down. The ally takes the other half and may survive at 1 HP or higher."}}
{"_id":"332d2a3b811a4188","name":"Deep Archive","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Kenta","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"I Read About This, Knowledge rank 4","description":"I Read About This now reveals two pieces of information instead of one on the same target."}}
{"_id":"9e0d5712bd94808a","name":"Tiny But Fierce","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Kenta","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Knowledge rank 4","description":"When your Digimon is attacked by a Digimon that is at a higher stage than yours, you may reduce the attacker's hit chance by 1, applied before the roll."}}
{"_id":"37bd392f7a27d27e","name":"Kotemon Wouldn't Have Been So Bad Either","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Kenta","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Deep Archive, Knowledge rank 5","description":"Once per session before any roll is made, you may declare that you have researched this specific situation. The GM must tell you the exact DN of the roll before you commit to attempting it."}}
{"_id":"28dd9ba4b07f49d3","name":"Heart Patter","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Kenta","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Tiny But Fierce, Knowledge rank 5","description":"Once per session as a Free Action, MarineAngemon bestows Heart Patter on one allied Digimon within 3 spaces. That Digimon immediately restores HP equal to your Knowledge rank x 3."}}
{"_id":"acee3fc93dfc715d","name":"Queen's Precision","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Rika","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Sincerity rank 3+)","description":"When your Digimon lands a hit, you may choose to forgo any status effect tags on the attack. If you do, deal +2 additional damage."}}
{"_id":"95d59bff0751c202","name":"Ice Wall","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Rika","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Sincerity rank 3+)","description":"Once per encounter as a Free Action after your Digimon is targeted by an attack — before the hit rolls — you may force the attacker to reroll their hit roll and take the lower result."}}
{"_id":"aaaad7eb88c77fe7","name":"Ruthless Efficiency","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Rika","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Sincerity rank 4","description":"When your Digimon defeats an enemy this encounter, they gain +2 to all attack rolls for the remainder of the encounter."}}
{"_id":"fca5bdc269b3a65f","name":"Cold Read","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Rika","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Sincerity rank 4","description":"Once per encounter as a Free Action on your turn, name a stat — Courage, Friendship, Love, Knowledge, Sincerity, or Reliability. The GM tells you whether the target enemy's total in that stat is lower than, equal to, or higher than your Digimon's total."}}
{"_id":"80206bba3fa822e2","name":"Digimon Queen","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Rika","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Ruthless Efficiency, Sincerity rank 5","description":"When your Digimon deals enough damage in a single hit to reduce a target to 0 HP, they may immediately make one additional Basic Attack against an adjacent enemy as a Free Action."}}
{"_id":"89a56a7d0db301cb","name":"I Don't Need Anyone","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Rika","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Ice Wall, Sincerity rank 5","description":"Ice Wall can now be used once per encounter against each individual enemy rather than once per encounter total. Once you know how someone fights the wall is always ready for them."}}
{"_id":"9ff57ba62402e57d","name":"Grudging Respect","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Rika","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 2 ability, Sincerity rank 5","description":"Once per session, choose one ally Digimon. Until the end of the encounter your Digimon and that ally each gain +2 to all damage rolls when within 3 spaces of each other."}}
{"_id":"2fe62b9b3620a224","name":"The Digimon Queen Needs No One. Except Maybe One Person.","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Rika","row":4,"expCost":1000,"requirements":"Any two Row 3 abilities, Sincerity rank 7","description":"Once per session at the start of your turn you may activate this ability. Your Digimon immediately gains temporary HP equal to your Sincerity rank x 4. While temporary HP remains your Digimon deals +4 bonus damage on all attacks. Temporary HP from this ability is lost before regular HP and is removed at end of encounter."}}
{"_id":"2f988386ac1e7d3f","name":"Legendary Status","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Ryo","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Courage rank 3+, at least one other stat rank 4+)","description":"Once per session when you enter an encounter, you may declare Legendary Status as a Free Action. One enemy of your choice — not a boss — immediately focuses their attention on your Digimon for the first two rounds, preferring to attack them over other targets when able."}}
{"_id":"260ae4f9f577f079","name":"Been Here Before","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Ryo","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Courage rank 3+, at least one other stat rank 4+)","description":"After you fail a skill check, add +3 to your result. This may turn a failure into a success."}}
{"_id":"3272f782edb4fd72","name":"Monodramon's Edge","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Ryo","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Courage rank 4","description":"Your Digimon's first attack each encounter automatically hits — no hit roll required."}}
{"_id":"5916ca430c4bf08c","name":"Tactical History","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Ryo","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Courage rank 4","description":"At the start of each encounter before turns begin, you may name one move type by tag — MELEE, RANGE, BURST, BLAST, CHARGE, or COUNTER. Until the end of the round your Digimon takes -2 damage from attacks with that tag."}}
{"_id":"8f0c03ec0b30ee6d","name":"The Long Road","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Ryo","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Monodramon's Edge, Courage rank 5","description":"Once per session at any point during an encounter, you may spend 10 Hope to immediately restore your Digimon to their current maximum Default Stage at full HP for that stage — even if the cascade has reduced their Default Stage below that point. After using this ability your Digimon cannot digivolve above their Default Stage for the rest of the session."}}
{"_id":"f2f873ae66f9b364","name":"Legendary Tamer","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Ryo","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Tactical History, Courage rank 5","description":"Legendary Status is now usable once per encounter instead of once per session. Additionally the focused enemy takes -2 to all attack rolls while Legendary Status is active and your Digimon is their primary target."}}
{"_id":"ddcb54ba76999366","name":"I've Already Won This Fight","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Ryo","row":4,"expCost":1000,"requirements":"Both Row 3 abilities, Courage rank 7","description":"Once per session after an enemy declares an attack but before any rolls are made, you may activate this ability. The attack misses automatically. No roll required."}}
{"_id":"813ae2861095cdc1","name":"Drawing Strength","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Takato","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Courage rank 3+)","description":"Once per session during a short rest, you may describe your Digimon performing a new technique you imagined for them. Until the next long rest your Digimon gains access to one additional move from their pool as a fifth active slot — it does not replace their signature move or any of their three learned moves. The move must be one your Digimon has access to at their current stage."}}
{"_id":"f685db26f11f2b72","name":"Never Give Up","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Takato","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Courage rank 3+)","description":"Once per encounter when your Digimon would fail an attack roll by 3 or less — falling just short of the hit threshold — the attack grazes. A graze deals half normal damage, bypasses no defences, and triggers no additional effects."}}
{"_id":"4d00375f5a2e9403","name":"Gogglehead's Resolve","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Takato","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Courage rank 4","description":"When your Digimon is at half HP or below they deal +3 bonus damage on all attacks."}}
{"_id":"f775fded3904b826","name":"Partner's Glow","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Takato","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Courage rank 4","description":"At the start of each of your turns, if your Digimon is digivolved above their Default Stage, you may spend 2 Hope to grant them +2 to their next attack roll AND +2 damage on that attack."}}
{"_id":"df53ff18bfba31b2","name":"Biomerge Ready","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Takato","row":3,"expCost":800,"requirements":"Both Row 2 abilities, Courage rank 6","description":"Your Tamer may now participate in Biomerge Digivolution. See Part 2: Rules for full details. Additionally, when you initiate Biomerge, the corruption check gains +2 to the roll."}}
